00:02:21.410 --> 00:02:24.770
Hello World that you start
every assignment with.

60
00:02:24.770 --> 00:02:28.130
If I say echo and then put
Hello World in quotes,

61
00:02:28.130 --> 00:02:30.650
I simply echo the content of

62
00:02:30.650 --> 00:02:34.410
the past back out
