00:02:34.940 --> 00:02:38.960
There's another I/O application

64
00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:41.270
that's really popular
and useful as cat.

65
00:02:41.270 --> 00:02:43.535
What cat is short
for concatenate,

66
00:02:43.535 --> 00:02:44.945
which means just print out

67
00:02:44.945 --> 00:02:48.565
whatever file that I specified
out to the terminal.

68
