97
00:03:58.790 --> 00:04:03.275
Some other common directory
in file manipulation,

98
00:04:03.275 --> 00:04:05.030
mv is going to move.

99
00:04:05.030 --> 00:04:08.120
So you can move files or
directories to a new location.

100
00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:10.255
Cp is going to copy.

101
00:04:10.255 --> 00:04:12.480
In the move case,
you're going to

102
00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:14.390
take the file out

