00:04:35.640 --> 00:04:39.020
If the file already exists or
if the file doesn't exist,

112
00:04:39.020 --> 00:04:41.120
it's just going to
create an empty file

113
00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:44.780
and update the timestamp
to the current timestamp.

